---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jamail Hardwoods Privacy Policy & SMS Messaging Terms"
  description="Jamail Hardwoods Privacy Policy and SMS Messaging Terms for website visitors and customers."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-ivory py-14 sm:py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-brand-sand/70 via-brand-ivory to-white pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-3xl bg-white/90 backdrop-blur p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-soft">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight text-brand-ink">
          Jamail Hardwoods Privacy Policy & SMS Messaging Terms
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/70">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-brand-ink/85 leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Introduction</h2>
            <p>
              This Privacy Policy explains how Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS) ("Jamail Hardwoods," "we," "us," or "our") collects,
              uses, and protects personal information provided by website visitors, customers, and individuals who communicate
              with us by phone, email, or SMS text message.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">SMS Messaging Disclosure</h2>
            <p>
              By providing your mobile phone number and opting in, you agree to receive SMS text messages from Jamail Hardwoods
              (FH TEXAS) at (832) 930-5936. SMS messages are sent only for account-related and customer service purposes,
              including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
              <li>Appointment confirmations and reminders</li>
              <li>Order and sample request updates</li>
              <li>Delivery notifications</li>
              <li>General customer service communications</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">Consent to receive SMS messages is not a condition of purchase.</p>
            <p>Message frequency varies and may be up to 4 messages per month.</p>
            <p>Message and data rates may apply.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">SMS Opt-In Process</h2>
            <p>Customers opt in to receive SMS messages by:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
              <li>Entering their phone number on our website forms at <a href="https://jamailfloors.com/contact/" class="text-brand-brass underline" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://jamailfloors.com/contact/</a></li>
              <li>Checking a box agreeing to receive SMS messages from Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">
              By opting in, customers expressly consent to receive SMS messages related to their relationship with
              Jamail Hardwoods.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">SMS Opt-Out & Help Instructions</h2>
            <p>To stop receiving SMS messages, reply STOP to any message at any time.</p>
            <p>For assistance, reply HELP or contact us using the information below.</p>
            <p>Opting out will stop all future SMS communications unless you re-subscribe.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">SMS Data Collection, Use & Retention</h2>
            <p>When you opt in to receive SMS messages, we collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
              <li>Your mobile phone number</li>
              <li>Your SMS consent</li>
              <li>The date and time of your opt-in</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">
              This information is used only to deliver SMS messages described in this policy. We retain SMS opt-in data for
              as long as you remain subscribed or as required by law.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">No Sharing of Mobile Opt-In Information</h2>
            <p>
              We do not sell, rent, transfer, or share mobile phone numbers, SMS consent, or opt-in data with third parties
              for marketing or promotional purposes. Any information sharing described elsewhere in this policy excludes
              mobile opt-in data.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Types of Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Name, email address, phone number, and postal/ZIP code</li>
              <li>Product interests and project details you provide</li>
              <li>Sample requests and design-related information</li>
              <li>Technical data such as IP address, browser type, and website usage</li>
              <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">
              Information is collected directly from you or through limited service providers supporting our operations.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Respond to inquiries and provide samples</li>
              <li>Process quotes, orders, and appointments</li>
              <li>Send SMS notifications if you have opted in</li>
              <li>Improve our website and customer experience</li>
              <li>Maintain internal records</li>
              <li>Protect our business and comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Data Security</h2>
            <p>
              We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Sample SMS Messages</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 1:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS): Your sample request has been received. We will notify you when it ships. Reply STOP to opt out.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 2:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS): Your appointment is confirmed for Friday at 10:00 AM. Reply HELP for assistance or STOP to opt out.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 3:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS): Your order is ready for delivery. Reply STOP to opt out.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">STOP Message Example</h2>
            <p>
              Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS): You have opted out of SMS messages and will receive no further texts.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">HELP Message Example</h2>
            <p>
              Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS): For assistance, call (832) 930-5936 or email info@jamailfloors.com.
              Reply STOP to opt out.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Cookies & Tracking</h2>
            <p>
              We use cookies to improve website functionality and analyze traffic. You may disable cookies in your browser
              settings, but some features may not function properly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Access your personal information</li>
              <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
              <li>Delete your personal information (where legally permitted)</li>
              <li>Withdraw SMS consent at any time by replying STOP</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-5">
              <p class="font-semibold">Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS)</p>
              <p>2643 Colquitt St</p>
              <p>Houston, TX 77098</p>
              <p class="mt-3">Phone & SMS: <a href="tel:+18329305936" class="text-brand-brass underline">(832) 930-5936</a></p>
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@jamailfloors.com" class="text-brand-brass underline">info@jamailfloors.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">SMS Campaign Description</h2>
            <p>
              Jamail Hardwoods (FH TEXAS) is a flooring and curated finishes showroom in Houston, Texas. SMS messages are used
              only for transactional and customer service communications, including appointment confirmations, order updates,
              delivery notifications, and related service messages. Message frequency varies and may be up to 4 messages per
              month. Message and data rates may apply. Mobile opt-in information is not shared with third parties.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
